import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import seaborn as sns
sns.set(font="Droid Sans",font_scale = 2)
sns.set_style("whitegrid")
sns.set_color_codes("dark")

data = pd.read_csv('data.csv', index_col=False)

hitData = data[['model', 'numIter', 'hit']].sort_values(['numIter'])
recallData = data[['model', 'numIter', 'Recall@10']].sort_values(['numIter'])
precData = data[['model', 'numIter', 'Prec@10']].sort_values(['numIter'])
nDCGData = data[['model', 'numIter', 'nDCG@10']].sort_values(['numIter'])
timeData = data[['model', 'numIter', 'learningTime']].sort_values(['numIter'])

plt.subplots(2,2,figsize=(15,15))
plt.subplot(2,2,1)
plt.plot(hitData[hitData['model'] == 'spark']['numIter'], hitData[hitData['model'] == 'spark']['hit'],  '-o', label='spark')
plt.plot(hitData[hitData['model'] == 'flink']['numIter'], hitData[hitData['model'] == 'flink']['hit'],  '-o', label='flink', color='red')
plt.legend(loc='lower right')
plt.title('Hits')
plt.xlabel('numIter')
plt.ylabel('hits')
plt.xlim(1,8)

plt.subplot(2,2,2)
plt.plot(nDCGData[nDCGData['model'] == 'spark']['numIter'], nDCGData[nDCGData['model'] == 'spark']['nDCG@10'],  '-o', label='spark')
plt.plot(nDCGData[nDCGData['model'] == 'flink']['numIter'], nDCGData[nDCGData['model'] == 'flink']['nDCG@10'],  '-o', label='flink', color='red')
plt.legend(loc='lower right')
plt.title('nDCG@10')
plt.xlabel('numIter')
plt.ylabel('nDCG@10')
plt.xlim(1,8)

plt.subplot(2,2,3)
plt.plot(precData[precData['model'] == 'spark']['numIter'], precData[precData['model'] == 'spark']['Prec@10'],  '-o', label='spark')
plt.plot(precData[precData['model'] == 'flink']['numIter'], precData[precData['model'] == 'flink']['Prec@10'],  '-o', label='flink', color='red')
plt.legend(loc='lower right')
plt.title('Prec@10')
plt.xlabel('numIter')
plt.ylabel('Prec@10')
plt.xlim(1,8)

plt.subplot(2,2,4)
plt.plot(recallData[recallData['model'] == 'spark']['numIter'], recallData[recallData['model'] == 'spark']['Recall@10'],  '-o', label='spark')
plt.plot(recallData[recallData['model'] == 'flink']['numIter'], recallData[recallData['model'] == 'flink']['Recall@10'],  '-o', label='flink', color='red')
plt.legend(loc='lower right')
plt.title('Recall@10')
plt.xlabel('numIter')
plt.ylabel('recall@10')
plt.xlim(1,8)

plt.tight_layout()
